author: Carol Robinson | crobinson@al.com
title: 'Predator' who posed as rapper to lure, rape women jailed again after new violent attack, police say
text: Aaron Hall, 21, was arrested by Gordo police, Tuscaloosa police and U.S. Marshals Saturday after lawmen say he lured a woman via a dating website to a parking lot where he raped her at knife-point.
